    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD model is accepted for the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Seven credibility factors were assessed and all demonstrated satisfactory performance. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The overall evidence package supports the conclusion that the model provides sufficient credibility for the comparative hemolysis evaluation.",
